text: Mossy Creek may refer to: *Mossy Creek (Chattahoochee River), a stream in Georgia *Mossy Creek, Georgia, an unincorporated community *Mossy Creek (Missouri), a stream in Missouri *Mossy Creek, Virginia, an unincorporated community *Mossy Creek, a district of Jefferson County, Tennessee, and the site of the Battle of Mossy Creek
title: Mossy Creek
